{"tid":1107282,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"[TG]90後無活動GP","createTime":"2019-04-15T06:36:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-26T15:27:27.000Z","uid":71606,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"75af8690fdd32acd74fa01da7c8be56ae4527412","tid":1107282,"uid":71606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T06:36:13.000Z","msg":"規舉入條LINK之後自己睇啦<br />\n睇過以上規舉，仲係想入既，就PM我。<br />\n等你地加入<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><a href=\"https://t.me/comehereifucan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fcomehereifucan&d=hmtFoPnP%2FIv5fOqUL3ZUasTiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=54cd3726\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/comehereifucan</a></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n有入GAME BOT<br />\n亦有全連登高登獨有KILLER玩(自創，無BOT，人手HOST)<br />\n亦有傳說對決團<br />\n<br />\n你亦可以分享下飲飲食食<br />\n朝流化妝<br />\n運動健身<br />\n有人識就會有人復你"},{"pid":"a0fb9ad7ee4ab33e50d1bcce3603398e19607764","tid":1107282,"uid":71606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T06:47:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b72785262296e7f2fe28372491773909eff70725","tid":1107282,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T06:57:35.000Z","msg":"我想學好中文 個group得唔得 得就<span style=\"color: red;\">覆</span>一<span style=\"color: red;\">覆</span>我"},{"pid":"8b2155bbedd64f008e54d56f4176d7c93f043811","tid":1107282,"uid":71606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T08:34:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02a5affac6521b6c1cfae38d2ed6fa6f12ff95cc","tid":1107282,"uid":71606,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"b72785262296e7f2fe28372491773909eff70725","tid":1107282,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T06:57:35.000Z","msg":"我想學好中文 個group得唔得 得就<span style=\"color: red;\">覆</span>一<span style=\"color: red;\">覆</span>我"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201